==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Nighly
<hw>Nigh"ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In a near relation in place,
time, degree, etc.; within a little; almost.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A cube and a sphere . . . <qex>nighly</qex> of the same
bigness.</q> <rj><qau>Locke.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Nighness</ent>⟦br⟧
